                  <rs id="t18780916-837-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18780916-837-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18780916-837-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp>, Unlawfully uttering counterfeit coin, to which</rs>
                  <persName id="def4-837-18780916" type="defendantName">
                     <interp inst="def4-837-18780916" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
