                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi>
                  </rs>. <hi rend="italic">They were further charged with having been convicted of a like offence in January</hi>, 1870, <hi rend="italic">at this Court, in the name of Henry and Ellen Bollin<lb></lb>son, to which they</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.—<rs id="t18780916-837-punishment-80" type="punishmentDescription">
